      "content": "i tried the heat thing and it doesnt help at all. i dont have any acetaminophen though. i have a whole bottle of aspirin here and some extra ibuprofen. i feel like i could take another 800mg of the ibuprofen now just to get through the night, would that be okay? i just really need the pain to stop so i can sleep.",
